{"tid":297701,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[實已證]猛毒、黑貓、銀貂與MCU無關","createTime":"2017-06-25T16:30:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-26T06:38:29.000Z","uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e28f2f1d8025b49dd83d49e712396c0431fb43ce","tid":297701,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T16:30:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/ErikDavis/status/878995450354913280\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FErikDavis%2Fstatus%2F878995450354913280&d=v5T9zA27hfXl6ZwND%2FyAWwRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=628aa878\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FErikDavis%2Fstatus%2F878995450354913280&h=96acaa8d\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/ErikDavis/status/878995450354913280</a><br />\n<br />\n繼Marvel Studios總裁凱文˙費吉（Kevin Feige）之後，Sony影業前主席艾美˙帕斯卡爾（Amy Pascal）稍早也針對自己幾天前的發言做出了澄清。經過連日來的風波，目前Marvel本家與Sony的對外說法已完全一致。<br />\nFadango稍早在《蜘蛛人：返校日》的記者會上向艾美求證，她表示自己必須更正先前的發言，目前兩家電影公司的合作範圍其實僅限於蜘蛛人（Spider-Man）這名角色，並不包含猛毒（Venom）、黑貓（Black Cat）、銀貂（Silver Sable）......這些未來將由Sony推出電影的蜘蛛人系列人物。<br />\n因此，這些本家未參與、由Sony獨力拍攝的電影都只屬於他們自己的另一個Marvel電影宇宙，不會與Marvel本家的電影世界觀Earth-199999有任何連結，也不會和《蜘蛛人：返校日》或《復仇者聯盟》系列電影有任何連動。"},{"pid":"2069419d70859fed09c6270d7877993236aa8ce4","tid":297701,"uid":110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T16:34:12.000Z","msg":"猛毒就話有d人識下姐 <br />\n黑貓呢d唔係追開漫畫冇乜人識都夠膽單獨拍獨立電影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7d3b274542a397a54998523033477797501efdb","tid":297701,"uid":60500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-25T16:36:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>猛毒就話有d人識下姐 <br />\n黑貓呢d唔係追開漫畫冇乜人識都夠膽單獨拍獨立電影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\ngotg未拍電影都冇乜人識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa01b0c927c1746cd9164529c7e9f4aa60300ce7","tid":297701,"uid":105567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"